'''阿耶洛有果菌属'''（学名：''Ajellomyces''）是[[阿耶洛双态菌科|阿耶洛双态菌科]]的一个属，其实是某些[[双态性真菌|双态性真菌]]在[[有性生殖|有性生殖]]相的{{le|有果形|teleomorph}}，目前包括荚膜阿耶洛有果菌、肥大阿耶洛有果菌与皮炎阿耶洛有果菌三个种，<ref>{{cite book|last=Sigler L.|title= Ajellomyces crescens sp. nov., taxonomy of Emmonsia spp., and relatedness with Blastomyces dermatitidis (teleomorph Ajellomyces dermatitidis) J Med Vet Mycol. 1996;34:303–14.|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8912163/}}</ref> <ref>{{cite book|last=Untereiner WA, Scott JA, Naveau FA, Sigler L, Bachewich J, Angus A (2004).|title="The Ajellomycetaceae, a new family of vertebrate-associated Onygenales". Mycologia. 96 (4): 812–821. doi:10.2307/3762114. JSTOR 3762114. PMID 21148901.|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/3762114?seq=1}}</ref>
它们分布广泛，特别是在热带地区。本属的{{le|无果形|anamorph}}之一就是著名的[[荚膜组织胞浆菌|荚膜组织胞浆菌]]，是[[组织胞浆菌病|组织胞浆菌病]]的致病菌。<ref>{{cite book|last=Rahim MA, Zaman S, Amin MR, Uddin KN, Ma JC.|title=Histoplasmosis: An Emerging or Neglected Disease in Bangladesh?  A Systematic Review. Oman Med J. 2020 Feb 16;35(1):e91. doi: 10.5001/omj.2020.09. PMID 32095275; PMCID: PMC7024808.|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32095275/}}</ref> 无果形[[荚膜组织胞浆菌|组织胞浆菌]]其实并没有[[荚膜|荚膜]]，只有[[阿耶洛有果菌属|阿耶洛有果菌属]]的{{le|有果形|teleomorph}}才有荚膜。<ref>{{cite book|last=Guimarães AJ, de Cerqueira MD, Nosanchuk JD (2011).|title="Surface architecture of Histoplasma capsulatum". Frontiers in Microbiology. 2: 225. doi:10.3389/fmicb.2011.00225. PMC 3220077. PMID 22121356.|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3220077/}}</ref>

